Imagine a Pest Control Agency basically becoming the biggest pests amongst their competition, as can be seen by their advertisements on COMPLETELY UNRELATED TOPICS (I mean seriously.. they were trying to advertise their terrible business on a Neurosurgery post..) and all of their reviews PRIOR to this one , have all been bot accounts, you can clearly tell solely by the ridiculous approach each posts takes..

If I could Rate negative, that is the only way id rate these scumbags. 1 Star is the best I can do.
